<p>The third release candidate (RC3) for WordPress 6.7 is ready for download and testing!</p>



<p><strong>This version of the WordPress software is under development</strong>.<strong> Please do not install, run, or test this version of WordPress on production or mission-critical websites.</strong> Instead, it‚Äôs recommended that you evaluate RC3 on a test server and site.</p>



<p>Reaching this phase of the release cycle is an important milestone. While release candidates are considered ready for release, testing remains crucial to ensure that everything in WordPress 6.7 is the best it can be.</p>



<p>You can test WordPress 6.7 RC3 in four ways:</p>



